    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>General term for ceremonial costume worn by kings, pelates, sacrificial victims, or other people for religious or other ceremonial or ritual purposes.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
